Package: dclone
Type: Package
Title: Data Cloning and MCMC Tools for Maximum Likelihood Methods
Version: 1.3-5
Date: 2011-08-23
Author: Peter Solymos
Maintainer: Peter Solymos <solymos@ualberta.ca>
Description: Low level functions for implementing
    maximum likelihood estimating procedures for 
    complex models using data cloning and Bayesian
    Markov chain Monte Carlo methods with support 
    for JAGS, WinBUGS and OpenBUGS.
    Parallel MCMC computations are supported
    and can result in nearly linear speed-up.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 2.7.0), coda (>= 0.13), R2WinBUGS, snow
Suggests: rjags, rlecuyer, rsprng, BRugs
Imports: stats
SystemRequirements: jags (>= 1.0.3), WinBUGS (>= 1.4)
URL: http://cran.r-project.org/package=dclone, http://dcr.r-forge.r-project.org/
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: true
